<subSubSection pageNumber="720" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageNumber="720">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="720">Note:</emphasis>
Evidently a 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="720">nomen novum</emphasis>
for 
<taxonomicName authority="L. (1753)" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Aira" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="indica">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="720">Aira indica</emphasis>
L. (1753)
</taxonomicName>
, the epithet being pre-occupied in 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Panicum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="720">Panicum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<taxonomicName authority="Mill. (1768)" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1768" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1753" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Panicum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="indicum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="720">P. indicum</emphasis>
Mill. (1768)
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authority="(L.) L. (1771)" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1768" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1753" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Panicum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="indicum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="720">P. indicum</emphasis>
(L.) L. (1771)
</taxonomicName>
is illegitimate as a consequence.
</paragraph>
